            <p>Parking has always been difficult to come by at Farmingdale, especially during rush hour. It may lead to lateness during class hours and unnecessary stress.
            This is why four students have come up with an application in order to fix this issue! RamPark has been created in order to simplify student life by providing 
            an easy to use parking interface that allows you to que up and wait for the next parking spot. No more endless searching and potential arguments!</p>
 
            <p>If you sign in using your Farmingdale e-mail login information, all of your information will automatically be pulled in, no need to full anything out!
            On top of that, users will be able to redeem a lifetime coupon for 50% off the parking permit! To begin using, please click the image on the right!</p>                
